Goal: Destroy the city in each of your opponent's zones

3 "Lines" (Rows)
5 "Zones" (Columns) per Side
Line closest to player is "City Line"
Next closest is the "Support Line"
And the furthest is the "Front Line"
Those on your side will be noted as "friendly"
Those on your opponent's will be noted as "enemy"

Placement Key Words
directly - one space from 
in front of - in a line further than and in same Zone
behind - in a line closer than and in same Zone
adjacent - in the same Line only
surrounding - next to in the same Line and in same Zone

Three Phases
Intel Phase-Draw Cards
Production Phase-Finish Production, Start New Productions
Activation Phase-Move, Fight and other Abilities



